        <abstract> 
<p>Suggests it would be easier and cheaper if he were given one or two pages in preface [to <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi>] for two or three important errors. Would like to take out one sentence if present preface is not stereotyped. Table of contents is shabby.</p> 
        </abstract>
